title: 73: The Target Haul Episode
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode
description: It’s everyone’s favorite store with a bullseye, Target! In this episode, Lisa and the gang CHEW & TELL over a dozen products from the big box store! Finds like reduced-fat ice cream, yogurt with nut butter, salsa, sparkling water, chicken, beef jerky, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, a new date & nut bar that’s a total game changer! So don’t go anywhere… Push play now, and after you listen, head over to our Foodcast page for more info on the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
